Package com.csse3200.game.components.slot

Class SlotEngine

java.lang.Object
com.csse3200.game.components.slot.SlotEngine
public class SlotEngine extends Object
Slot machine engine to generate random outcomes for UI and trigger corresponding effects.

Flow: 1) Roll trigger (default 80%). 2) If triggered, pick an event by weights and return triple reels of that event id. Otherwise, return a non-triple reels array. 3) Effect handling

* Output for UI: * - SpinResult#getReels(): int[3] of ids in [0..7] * - SpinResult#isEffectTriggered(): boolean * - SpinResult#getEffect():Optional&lt;Effect&gt;

New: Spin Credits * Start with 5 credits by default (configurable). * Automatically +1 credit every 5 seconds (configurable). * spin() consumes 1 credit each time. * When no credits left, return a non-triple result with no effect, and log a warning.
